
berb-github-repo-mgr (0.0.2) devel; urgency=low

  [ Berbascum ]
  * New: fn_get_repo_info: Unified in this function getting repo information.
  * New: fn_msg_branch_confirm: Implemented ask for confirmation before some
    actions.
  * New: Now the script gets organization name from parent dir name. Requires
    next dir structure:
    Ex. <repos_path>/<organization_name>/<project_name>
  * Add: The functions fn_pull, fn_push and fn_commit_all call at start
    the function fn_msg_branch_confirm.
  * Add: Implemented commit multiline comments using vim.
  * Add: changelog file creation in debian format.
  * Add: info-deb-package.sh file for deb packging.
  * Cut: Removed changelog from script.
  * Remove: fn_precheck_repo_nom: No more needed.
  * Optimize: Renamed vars:
    REPO_ACCOUNT to ORG_NAME and REPO_NAME to PROJECT_NAME
  * Mark: Marked some functions as "TODO" and "NEED REVISION"
  * Release version 0.0.2 devel

 -- Berbascum <berbascum@ticv.cat>  Tue,  01 Nov 2022 15:00:00 +0100


